<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287937>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Penis in ventral, lateral and dorsal view of apex of the species Calligrapha ancoralis Stål (a, d), C. anabelae sp. nov. (b, e), C. catarinae sp. nov. (c, f), C. ramulifera Stål (g, h), and C. argus Stål (i, j). Scale bar = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287937/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287936>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Geographic distributions of Calligrapha ancoralis Stål (black circles) and the two new species of Calligrapha described here, C. anabelae sp. nov. (white squares) and C. catarinae sp. nov. (black squares)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287936/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3539691>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Phenotypic variation in Calligrapha anabelae sp. nov. Top row (from left to right): Holotype (MfN), Paratype 1 (MfN) and Paratype 3 (NHM); bottom row (from left to right): Paratype 2 (MfN), Paratype 5 (NHM) and Paratype 4 (NHM)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3539691/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

